---
title: Savoury Nut and Herb-Crusted Cheese Ball as an extra Serves 2
description: A savoury herb and nut-crusted cheese ball is the perfect party or weeknight appetizer. Grab a knife and spread some on the toasted garlic flatbread wedges for a delicious treat!
